m_q.target_metric: Latest year where Real Colorado Foxes did not qualify for playoffs but reached Open Cup 2nd Round
sub_questions: Which years did the team not qualify for playoffs?
Which years did the team reach Open Cup 2nd Round?
What is the intersection of these two conditions?
What is the maximum/latest year from this intersection?

unit_annotations.Open Cup: tournament round reached or qualification status

format_notes: Year column contains string representations of years
Playoffs column contains either playoff round names or 'Did not qualify'
Open Cup column contains tournament rounds ('1st Round', '2nd Round') or 'Did not qualify' or 'Canceled'
Regular Season contains ordinal position and division name

constraints: Year must be parseable as integer for comparison
Playoffs value must exactly match 'Did not qualify'
Open Cup value must exactly match '2nd Round'
Result must be a single year value
derived_filters: Filter rows where Playoffs column equals 'Did not qualify' AND Open Cup column equals '2nd Round'
From filtered rows, select the maximum Year value
output_format_requirements: Return the latest (maximum) year as a single value
Year should be returned as integer or year format
